import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useNavigate, Link } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Container, Typography, Card, CardContent, Button, Select, MenuItem, FormControl, InputLabel, Grid, IconButton, List, ListItem, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'; import { Menu as MenuIcon, ExitToApp as ExitToAppIcon, AccountBalanceWallet as AccountBalanceWalletIcon, Group as GroupIcon, GroupAdd as GroupAddIcon, AccountCircle as AccountCircleIcon, Rule as RuleIcon, HelpOutline as HelpOutlineIcon, Security as SecurityIcon, Assignment as AssignmentIcon } from '@mui/icons-material'; import FooterMenu from '../Footer.jsx'; import './Team.css'; const Team = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [menuOpen, setMenuOpen] = useState(false); const [filter, setFilter] = useState('All'); const [teamData, setTeamData] = useState({ registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, cumulativeTeamSize: 0, generations: [ { percentage: 18, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, { percentage: 6, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, { percentage: 3, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00 }, ] }); const toggleMenu = () => setMenuOpen(!menuOpen); const handleFilterChange = (e) => setFilter(e.target.value); const handleViewTeamList = () => navigate('/team-list'); const logout = () => { // Implement your logout logic console.log("Logging out..."); }; return (
{/* Header */}
{/* Side Menu */}
{/* Main Content */} My Team {/* Filter Section */} My Team Overview Filter {/* Overview Cards */} Registered Members {teamData.registeredMembers} Valid Members {teamData.validMembers} Team Income ${teamData.teamIncome.toFixed(2)} {/* Team Size & Button */} Cumulative Team Size: {teamData.cumulativeTeamSize} {/* Generations Data */} The Last Three Generations of Data {teamData.generations.map((gen, index) => ( Generation {index + 1} Percentage: {gen.percentage}% Team Commission: ${gen.teamCommission} Registered Members: {gen.registeredMembers} Valid Members: {gen.validMembers} Team Income: ${gen.teamIncome.toFixed(2)} ))}
{/* Footer */}
); }; export default Team;
